          <source>The <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.Drawing.Graphics&gt;</ph> object provides the <ph id="ph2">&lt;xref:System.Drawing.Graphics.DrawLine%2A&gt;</ph> method, and the <ph id="ph3">&lt;xref:System.Drawing.Pen&gt;</ph> object stores features of the line, such as color and width.</source>
